headline: Wells Fargo initiates coverage of chip stocks; ON Semiconductor, Arm at Overweight
summary: Investing.com -- Wells Fargo initiated coverage on a range of semiconductor stocks on Friday, highlighting key opportunities and challenges across the sector.
